commit.message:
fix(depot-map): Add working MapLibre GL implementation

- Replace SVG-based map with proper MapLibre GL map
- Use OpenStreetMap tiles for base layer
- Fix TypeScript errors with allocation properties
- Add proper track rendering with polylines
- Add train markers with popups
- Add debug logging for troubleshooting
- Fix coordinate system for Essingen and Langweid depots
- Add error handling and loading states
